---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import {
	SITE_TITLE,
	SITE_DESCRIPTION,
	SITE_AUTHOR,
	SITE_EMAIL,
} from "../consts";
---

<Layout title={`About — ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<section class="about">
		<h1>About {SITE_TITLE}</h1>

		<p class="intro">
			{SITE_AUTHOR} is an independent development team based in the United States.
			We build small, focused apps that do exactly what they promise — nothing
			more, nothing less.
		</p>

		<h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
		<p>
			The App Store is full of apps that are free to download but
			expensive to actually use — padded with subscriptions, ads, nagging
			notifications, and tracking you didn't ask for. {SITE_TITLE} exists as
			a reaction to that. Every app we build is guided by a simple set of principles:
		</p>

		<ul class="principles">
			<li>
				<strong>Do one thing well.</strong> A focused app that solves a real
				problem beats a bloated app that tries to do everything.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>Respect your privacy.</strong> Your data belongs to you. Our
				apps don't run ads, and we don't sell personal data. When we use
				analytics, they are limited to product-improvement signals, are not
				used for advertising or cross-app profiling, and do not include
				personally identifiable information.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>No subscriptions for simple things.</strong> If an app doesn't
				cost us money to run, it shouldn't cost you money every month to use.
				We prefer one-time purchases and free tiers instead of needless recurring
				fees.
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>No dark patterns.</strong> No manipulative review prompts,
				no artificial feature restrictions designed to upsell, no notification
				spam. Just an app that works.
			</li>
			<li class="closing">
				In short — apps you'd be comfortable recommending to your
				parents. Genuinely easy to use, honestly priced, and designed
				for real people, not for extracting maximum revenue from them.
			</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Get in Touch</h2>
		<p>
			Questions, feedback, or just want to say hello — reach us at{" "}
			<a href={`mailto:${SITE_EMAIL}`}>{SITE_EMAIL}</a>.
		</p>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		max-width: 42rem;
	}

	.about h1 {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.intro {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		opacity: 0.85;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.about h2 {
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.about a {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.principles {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 1.25rem 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.principles li {
		padding-left: 1rem;
		border-left: 3px solid var(--accent, #4f46e5);
	}

	.principles li.closing {
		border-left-color: transparent;
		opacity: 0.75;
		font-style: italic;
	}
</style>
